node.text: Our latest mural will have you seeing stars 🤩 This intergalactic mural was painted by the ultimate #7ElevenSpaceInvader @lilfinehoney in Michigan (the Slurpee capital of the US!) to commemorate the launch site of the first Slurpee delivered to SPACE 💫 You read that right. Would you drink a Slurpee that's been to space and back? @ammersiongroup #SlurpeeSpaceDelivery
